## APPEND WORKFLOW

After Gemini outputs the JSON for a video, you have two options:

### Option A: Manual Append
Copy the JSON object and paste it into your growing dataset file:

```json
// director_training_dataset.jsonl (one object per line)
{"source": {"title": "LTX 2.3 Advanced Techniques"...}, "techniques": [...], ...}
{"source": {"title": "Veo 3.1 Prompt Masterclass"...}, "techniques": [...], ...}
```

### Option B: Gemini-Managed Append
Say to Gemini: "Add this to the running dataset" — and it will maintain
the growing array in its context. When you're done for the session, say
"Export the full dataset" and it will output the complete array.

### Option C: Google Drive Append (if using Gemini with Drive)
"Append this entry to my file director_training_data.jsonl in Google Drive"

