## QUICK COMMANDS (say these to Gemini while watching)

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| "Extract training data from this video" | Full extraction using the schema above |
| "Just the prompts from this video" | Only the prompt_examples array |
| "What are the anti-patterns here?" | Focus on what NOT to do |
| "Training pairs only" | Just the instruction/response pairs for fine-tuning |
| "Add to dataset" | Appends to the running session dataset |
| "Export full dataset" | Outputs everything collected this session |
| "How many entries so far?" | Count of videos processed this session |

